## Screenshot Guidelines

- **Format:** PNG for UI, JPG for photos
- **Size:** Optimize to < 500 KB
- **Resolution:** 1920x1080 or smaller
- **Crop:** Show only relevant UI elements
- **Annotations:** Use red arrows/boxes to highlight important areas
- **Alt text:** Always include descriptive alt text in MDX files

## Tools

- **macOS:** Command+Shift+4 (crop select)
- **Windows:** Snipping Tool or Win+Shift+S
- **Linux:** Screenshot utility (varies by distro)
- **Optimize:** Use TinyPNG.com or ImageOptim

